<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Ticket #{{ticketId}} Resolved</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #4a90e2; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #777; text-align: center; }
        .ticket-info { background: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Your Ticket Has Been Resolved</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello,</p>
            <p>We're pleased to inform you that your support ticket has been resolved.</p>
            
            <div class="ticket-info">
                <h3>Ticket #{{ticketId}}: {{title}}</h3>
                {{#if resolutionNotes}}
                <p><strong>Resolution Notes:</strong></p>
                <p>{{resolutionNotes}}</p>
                {{/if}}
                <p><strong>Resolved On:</strong> {{resolvedAt}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>If you have any further questions or need additional assistance, please don't hesitate to reply to this email.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Crossover Helpdesk Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>Â© 2025 Crossover Helpdesk. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
